大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"defe093561926fb8b5a0c58b1ebfa1d4239844da","tid":1541714,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:55:57.000Z","msg":"杯葛香港 你我有責"},{"pid":"fdb9e48ad37ac0307406e5995c31cb8cb9bd59b5","tid":1541714,"uid":171561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:00:40.000Z","msg":"杯葛香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 建議中共對香港唔好管 咩都唔好理 由佢自生自滅"},{"pid":"3e2887259192f15f3e7ef5c875a032b5cb970728","tid":1541714,"uid":76184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:00:44.000Z","msg":"推啊屌 咪撚柒再嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想尖沙咀上水下個禮拜又人頭湧湧一陣支那臭味啊仆街"},{"pid":"e49e13f5f7a9719fa018ebaed5bafc8b82b70c1d","tid":1541714,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:03:57.000Z","msg":"要香港永不超生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a